00:15:09,550 --> 00:15:10,550
Team A reporting.

296
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:12,200
Drug makers are basically under control.

297
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:13,420
The target boss is not seen.

298
00:15:13,420 --> 00:15:14,880
Okay, Cangfeng has been found.

299
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:15,790
All teams, attention.

300
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:17,120
Focus on searching for the prime culprit.

301
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,550
Make sure to catch He Wu.

302
00:15:18,670 --> 00:15:19,200
Yes, sir.

303
00:15:19,740 --> 00:15:21,270
He Wu hasn't been found yet?

304
00:15:21,450 --> 00:15:22,380
We will find him.

305
00:15:24,110 --> 00:15:25,580
Surveillance team 1, Surveillance team 1.

306
00:15:25,580 --> 00:15:26,130
Copy that.

307
00:15:26,130 --> 00:15:27,930
Bring Comrade Jiang Cheng back.

308
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:31,080
Copy that.

309
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:34,970
Let's go.

310
00:15:43,790 --> 00:15:44,720
Feeling better?

311
00:15:46,100 --> 00:15:46,770
Junior,

312
00:15:46,800 --> 00:15:47,680
leave him to me.

313
00:15:48,870 --> 00:15:49,600
Jiang Cheng,

314
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,590
you are suspected
of murdering the 8/17 Case

315
00:15:51,590 --> 00:15:53,060
task force leader Yao Weihai

316
00:15:53,060 --> 00:15:54,440
and officer Meng Junfeng.

317
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:57,100
Please come back
with us for the investigation.

318
00:16:00,490 --> 00:16:02,290
I know you're feeling terrible,

319
00:16:02,680 --> 00:16:04,640
but we have to follow the rules.

320
00:16:05,300 --> 00:16:06,900
You can talk when we get back.

321
00:16:11,550 --> 00:16:12,030
Okay.

322
00:16:16,520 --> 00:16:17,190
I'm sorry.

323
00:16:21,270 --> 00:16:22,030
Jiang Cheng!

324
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:23,240
Jiang Cheng.

325
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:25,380
Jiang Cheng!

326
00:16:25,560 --> 00:16:26,980
Jiang Cheng, open the door!

327
00:16:26,980 --> 00:16:27,860
Jiang Cheng!

328
00:16:39,490 --> 00:16:40,570
You left me here.

329
00:16:41,260 --> 00:16:43,060
You want to sacrifice me, right?

330
00:16:43,450 --> 00:16:45,380
I've destroyed the surveillance.

331
00:16:45,630 --> 00:16:46,750
Tell me right now,

332
00:16:47,250 --> 00:16:49,180
how am I supposed to get out of here?

333
00:16:53,030 --> 00:16:55,270
Split up. One on each side.

334
00:17:27,800 --> 00:17:28,510
He Wu!

335
00:17:28,540 --> 00:17:29,780
You won't escape.

336
00:17:30,360 --> 00:17:31,120
Jiang Cheng!

337
00:17:32,750 --> 00:17:34,240
I trusted you so much,

338
00:17:34,310 --> 00:17:36,310
but you actually betrayed your bro?

339
00:17:36,350 --> 00:17:37,640
Who's your bro?

340
00:17:38,790 --> 00:17:39,440
He Wu.

341
00:17:39,740 --> 00:17:41,740
I advise you not to walk into a dead end.

342
00:17:41,740 --> 00:17:42,940
If you surrender now,

343
00:17:42,950 --> 00:17:44,920
you still have a chance
to atone for your sins.

344
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:45,880
Atone?

345
00:17:46,220 --> 00:17:47,680
What's the use of atoning?

346
00:17:48,290 --> 00:17:49,680
But you, Jiang Cheng,

347
00:17:51,030 --> 00:17:51,830
go to hell

348
00:17:51,830 --> 00:17:53,640
and atone to my brother He Wen.

349
00:17:54,830 --> 00:17:55,680
He

350
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:57,680
treated you like a real brother.

351
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:59,950
Before he died,
he even asked me to take care of you.

352
00:17:59,950 --> 00:18:00,740
But you?

353
00:18:01,370 --> 00:18:02,720
Did you do right by him?

354
00:18:03,590 --> 00:18:04,350
And,

355
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:07,010
you can't explain
Yao Weihai's death.

356
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:09,690
And Junfeng.

357
00:18:10,150 --> 00:18:11,550
They are all dead now!

358
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:14,970
You, an undercover cop,

359
00:18:15,510 --> 00:18:17,110
are really interesting.

360
00:18:20,030 --> 00:18:21,000
For 5 years...

361
00:18:21,350 --> 00:18:23,550
For 5 whole years, I called you brother.

362
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,580
And now you're here to kill me.

363
00:18:26,110 --> 00:18:26,880
Okay.

364
00:18:27,750 --> 00:18:30,810
Today, I will send you,
the undercover cop, on your way!

365
00:19:04,830 --> 00:19:06,310
Surveillance team 1, Surveillance team 1.

366
00:19:06,310 --> 00:19:07,640
Report your situation.

367
00:19:08,110 --> 00:19:09,550
Surveillance team 1, Surveillance team 1.

368
00:19:09,550 --> 00:19:10,880
Report your situation.

369
00:19:11,710 --> 00:19:14,110
Surveillance team 1, Surveillance team 1.

370
00:21:02,150 --> 00:21:04,550
Tell me where Old Scorpion is!

371
00:21:12,570 --> 00:21:13,570
Stop laughing!

372
00:21:30,240 --> 00:21:31,570
Hold on tight!

373
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:40,320
Jiang Cheng.

374
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:43,200
Grab it.

375
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:18,130
Hurry. Let's go.

376
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:21,440
Are you okay?

377
00:22:27,210 --> 00:22:28,540
Hold on a little longer.

378
00:22:28,860 --> 00:22:29,400
Almost...

379
00:22:29,400 --> 00:22:30,200
Almost there.

380
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:31,130
Jiang Cheng!

381
00:22:31,240 --> 00:22:31,970
Jiang Cheng!

382
00:22:32,030 --> 00:22:32,920
Jiang Cheng.

383
00:22:33,110 --> 00:22:33,770
Jiang Cheng.

384
00:22:33,770 --> 00:22:34,360
Jiang Cheng.

385
00:22:34,360 --> 00:22:35,320
Jiang Cheng.

386
00:22:36,080 --> 00:22:36,680
Found him!

387
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:38,030
Hurry! Hurry.

388
00:22:38,140 --> 00:22:38,900
Over here.

389
00:22:38,980 --> 00:22:39,660
Hurry up.

390
00:22:40,030 --> 00:22:41,000
Hurry up.

391
00:22:41,540 --> 00:22:42,300
Careful.

392
00:22:44,030 --> 00:22:44,790
Lift him up.

393
00:23:00,240 --> 00:23:01,370
Hold his hands down.

394
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:15,610
Zhou Jin.

395
00:23:16,940 --> 00:23:17,590
Mentor.

396
00:23:23,030 --> 00:23:24,090
There's something

397
00:23:24,790 --> 00:23:26,350
I have to make clear to you.

398
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:31,200
Because your relationship
with Jiang Cheng is special,

399
00:23:31,200 --> 00:23:32,920
you can't participate in

400
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:35,690
the following investigation.

401
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:37,010
This is discipline.

402
00:23:37,510 --> 00:23:38,240
Understand?

403
00:23:38,720 --> 00:23:39,520
I understand.

404
00:23:39,680 --> 00:23:40,940
I'll keep my distance.

405
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:42,510
This case

406
00:23:42,540 --> 00:23:45,270
is under heavy scrutiny
from all sides right now.

407
00:23:45,510 --> 00:23:46,920
And he is a key witness

408
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:48,030
in this case.

409
00:23:48,270 --> 00:23:49,480
So the subsequent investigation

410
00:23:49,480 --> 00:23:51,080
might be quite complicated.

411
00:23:53,720 --> 00:23:55,180
Have you told your parents

412
00:23:56,480 --> 00:23:57,590
about Jiang Cheng?

413
00:23:58,830 --> 00:23:59,720
Not yet.

414
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:01,240
I want to wait

415
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:02,830
until the investigation is over

416
00:24:02,830 --> 00:24:04,110
and everything is clear

417
00:24:04,110 --> 00:24:05,170
before I tell them.

418
00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:07,890
That's good.

419
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:12,250
How is Professor Jiang?

420
00:24:12,750 --> 00:24:13,720
What's wrong with him?

421
00:24:13,720 --> 00:24:16,780
He had a fever and took leave to go home.
Didn't you know?

422
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:17,680
He had a fever?

423
00:24:17,870 --> 00:24:18,670
Look at you.

424
00:24:18,690 --> 00:24:20,280
Why are you asking me?

425
00:24:20,310 --> 00:24:21,750
You are his wife.

426
00:24:21,750 --> 00:24:22,760
Alright, don't just stand there.

427
00:24:22,760 --> 00:24:23,890
Hurry up and go home.

428
00:24:31,590 --> 00:24:32,240
Hansheng.

429
00:24:46,990 --> 00:24:47,710
Hansheng.

430
00:25:19,140 --> 00:25:20,380
Why did you drink?

431
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:22,800
Just a little.

432
00:25:26,040 --> 00:25:27,850
Do you come back to get something?

433
00:25:27,850 --> 00:25:28,780
What do you need?

434
00:25:28,830 --> 00:25:29,890
I'll get it for you.

435
00:25:30,880 --> 00:25:32,740
Why would I need to get something?

436
00:25:35,570 --> 00:25:37,710
Aren't you bringing a change of clothes?

437
00:25:37,710 --> 00:25:38,990
I'm not on duty today.

438
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:40,790
Mentor said you had a fever.

439
00:25:40,790 --> 00:25:42,390
I rushed back to check on you.

440
00:25:57,680 --> 00:25:59,480
Why aren't you saying anything?

441
00:25:59,930 --> 00:26:01,060
Are you drunk?

442
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:25,090
Don't move. Behave.

443
00:26:32,500 --> 00:26:34,030
Did you take your medicine?

444
00:26:35,300 --> 00:26:35,930
I did.

445
00:26:37,690 --> 00:26:39,220
I woke up drenched in sweat,

446
00:26:39,850 --> 00:26:40,880
so I took a shower.

447
00:26:43,930 --> 00:26:44,890
You're sick,

448
00:26:44,920 --> 00:26:46,030
and you still drank.

449
00:26:46,030 --> 00:26:47,640
Then you took medicine after drinking,

450
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:49,480
and even took a shower with a fever?

451
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:50,410
Jiang Hansheng,

452
00:26:50,970 --> 00:26:52,450
do you have a death wish?

453
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,170
How is it?

454
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:01,500
Don't you know if you have a fever?

455
00:27:10,280 --> 00:27:11,240
37.6 degrees.

456
00:27:11,500 --> 00:27:12,430
It's a low fever.

457
00:27:19,070 --> 00:27:20,730
You didn't even dry your hair.

458
00:27:22,090 --> 00:27:24,750
Don't you know
you'll have a headache tomorrow?

459
00:27:54,740 --> 00:27:56,420
I'll make you tomato and eggs,

460
00:27:56,460 --> 00:27:59,320
and maybe some stir-fried pork
with green peppers.

461
00:27:59,460 --> 00:28:02,460
Anything more complicated than that,
I can't handle.

462
00:28:05,110 --> 00:28:07,040
Are you going to eat with me at home?

463
00:28:09,350 --> 00:28:11,210
You're not going to the hospital?

464
00:28:12,370 --> 00:28:13,900
I just came back from there.

465
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:23,020
How is Jiang Cheng?

466
00:28:25,350 --> 00:28:26,350
He's fine.

467
00:28:26,850 --> 00:28:28,350
There's someone taking care of him.

468
00:28:28,350 --> 00:28:30,080
I should keep my distance, too.

469
00:28:58,440 --> 00:28:59,400
Are you drunk,

470
00:29:00,290 --> 00:29:01,820
or are you not feeling well?

471
00:29:09,140 --> 00:29:10,140
It is boiling.

472
00:29:14,380 --> 00:29:15,310
Jiang Hansheng.

473
00:29:15,830 --> 00:29:16,480
I'm here.

474
00:29:18,720 --> 00:29:20,330
If you keep hugging me like this,

475
00:29:20,330 --> 00:29:20,860
we're going to have another case

476
00:29:20,860 --> 00:29:23,320
of carbon monoxide poisoning
in this house.

477
00:29:44,310 --> 00:29:46,370
If you want to talk about Jiang Cheng,

478
00:29:46,550 --> 00:29:47,550
you can talk to me.

479
00:29:49,410 --> 00:29:50,170
I don't mind.

480
00:29:53,660 --> 00:29:54,590
I'm fine.

481
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:55,640
Really.

482
00:30:05,110 --> 00:30:06,040
Jiang Hansheng.

483
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:09,310
Are you angry?

484
00:30:09,550 --> 00:30:10,720
Of course I am.

485
00:30:11,550 --> 00:30:12,680
You can bite me back.

486
00:30:13,120 --> 00:30:14,560
Why would I bite you?

487
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:16,810
Zhou Jin,

488
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:20,370
you can treat me without any scruples.

489
00:30:20,540 --> 00:30:21,830
You can say whatever you want

490
00:30:21,830 --> 00:30:23,230
and do whatever you want.

491
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:25,240
Anything is fine.

492
00:30:27,780 --> 00:30:30,440
You don't need to consider
whether I can bear it.

493
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:31,960
I'm your husband.

494
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:34,850
We're married—we should be like this.

495
00:30:35,310 --> 00:30:36,240
No holding back,

496
00:30:36,840 --> 00:30:39,640
no pretending.
You don't have to hold back with me.

497
00:30:41,310 --> 00:30:42,030
So,

498
00:30:42,420 --> 00:30:44,030
you can do whatever you want.

499
00:30:45,110 --> 00:30:46,110
It's just that...

500
00:30:47,540 --> 00:30:48,500
it really hurts.

501
00:30:56,130 --> 00:30:56,990
It was my fault.

502
00:30:57,690 --> 00:30:58,750
It was my fault.

503
00:31:00,070 --> 00:31:01,330
That's not your fault.

504
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:03,080
There are some things

505
00:31:03,780 --> 00:31:04,930
I might not do well.

506
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:10,000
But you do many things very well.

507
00:31:11,590 --> 00:31:12,480
You are calm,

508
00:31:12,750 --> 00:31:13,440
sharp,

509
00:31:14,580 --> 00:31:15,380
and talented.

510
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:20,340
There are many things
that seem very difficult,

511
00:31:20,510 --> 00:31:21,480
but with you,

512
00:31:22,480 --> 00:31:24,210
you can always find a solution.

513
00:31:29,230 --> 00:31:30,120
I'm greedy.

514
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:10,930
It's not this pocket watch.

515
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:13,890
I've seen a more beautiful one.

516
00:32:15,560 --> 00:32:16,950
On that pocket watch,

517
00:32:19,630 --> 00:32:21,430
there was a pine branch pattern.

518
00:32:22,130 --> 00:32:23,590
It was polished brightly.

519
00:32:25,350 --> 00:32:27,210
Inside it, there was a little girl

520
00:32:28,750 --> 00:32:30,550
smiling at you with curved eyes.

521
00:32:33,220 --> 00:32:35,420
I think this one is also very beautiful.

522
00:32:36,700 --> 00:32:38,110
Can you show it to me?

523
00:32:38,480 --> 00:32:39,270
No,

524
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:40,510
it's not beautiful enough.

525
00:32:40,510 --> 00:32:41,370
It's not right.

526
00:32:42,190 --> 00:32:43,190
It's not right.

527
00:32:44,570 --> 00:32:46,300
It's not good-looking enough.

528
00:32:47,650 --> 00:32:49,110
Not good-looking enough.

529
00:32:49,510 --> 00:32:50,350
Did I

530
00:32:50,350 --> 00:32:52,510
do something to upset you?

531
00:32:57,710 --> 00:32:59,990
I asked you to investigate Jiang Cheng.

532
00:33:01,200 --> 00:33:03,390
But you didn't find out that Jiang Cheng

533
00:33:03,390 --> 00:33:04,700
knows Officer Zhou?

534
00:33:05,750 --> 00:33:07,830
Or did you know Jiang Cheng had a problem

535
00:33:07,830 --> 00:33:10,100
but didn't tell me?

536
00:33:11,430 --> 00:33:12,430
Y-you should

537
00:33:13,300 --> 00:33:15,410
ask Boss He about him.

538
00:33:16,170 --> 00:33:17,640
Do you like Jiang Cheng?

539
00:33:18,990 --> 00:33:19,920
He's quite cute.

540
00:33:20,130 --> 00:33:22,190
Really, I also think he's quite cute.

541
00:33:22,310 --> 00:33:22,930
Tell me the truth.

542
00:33:22,930 --> 00:33:23,830
Don't be like this.

543
00:33:23,830 --> 00:33:24,830
Tell me the truth.

544
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:28,160
This is not the answer I want!

545
00:33:30,200 --> 00:33:32,720
You lied to me.

546
00:33:45,880 --> 00:33:46,940
As expected of you.

547
00:33:47,860 --> 00:33:48,970
That's enough.

548
00:33:50,090 --> 00:33:51,160
Don't push me.

549
00:34:03,140 --> 00:34:03,960
You know what?

550
00:34:04,850 --> 00:34:07,090
Only you dare to treat me like this.

551
00:34:14,219 --> 00:34:14,820
Qiu Ye.

552
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:17,000
Do you know why,

553
00:34:18,330 --> 00:34:20,389
no matter what huge mistake you make,

554
00:34:21,100 --> 00:34:22,560
I will always forgive you?

555
00:34:24,440 --> 00:34:25,070
I'm sorry.

556
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,040
I'm tired.

557
00:34:40,590 --> 00:34:41,360
I'm tired.

558
00:34:47,420 --> 00:34:48,139
Tired.

559
00:34:52,159 --> 00:34:56,150
[Three days later]

560
00:35:03,520 --> 00:35:06,070
Jiang Cheng's interrogation
should have started.

561
00:35:06,070 --> 00:35:07,200
I heard it's at 9:30.

562
00:35:10,030 --> 00:35:11,590
Zhao Ping and I went to Jingzhou.

563
00:35:11,590 --> 00:35:12,860
We missed so much.

564
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:15,530
We didn't participate
in such a big operation at all.

565
00:35:15,530 --> 00:35:16,490
What a pity.

566
00:35:17,640 --> 00:35:19,900
What has Zhao Ping been busy with lately?

567
00:35:20,190 --> 00:35:22,450
He's sorting out the materials
for the Crime Research Lab.

568
00:35:22,450 --> 00:35:23,340
Director Wang

569
00:35:23,370 --> 00:35:24,970
writes a lot of things by hand

570
00:35:25,120 --> 00:35:26,030
and on those

571
00:35:26,030 --> 00:35:27,320
lined papers.

572
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:29,690
The handwriting is so wild
that it's almost as hard to read

573
00:35:29,690 --> 00:35:31,220
as a doctor's handwriting.

574
00:35:32,040 --> 00:35:34,470
Chief Tan asked him
to sort them out and print them.

575
00:35:34,470 --> 00:35:36,400
That will keep him busy for a while.

576
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:46,360
Behave yourself.

577
00:35:46,590 --> 00:35:47,240
Sit down.

578
00:35:50,570 --> 00:35:51,250
Are you messing around?

579
00:35:51,250 --> 00:35:52,510
Where are you looking?

580
00:35:53,710 --> 00:35:54,670
We brought you here today

581
00:35:54,670 --> 00:35:55,510
to ask about

582
00:35:55,510 --> 00:35:57,930
Jiang Cheng's situation
while he was serving his sentence.

583
00:35:57,930 --> 00:35:59,690
I heard you are very familiar
with him, right?

584
00:35:59,690 --> 00:36:00,730
Jiang Cheng?

585
00:36:01,370 --> 00:36:02,970
T-Then let me ask in advance.

586
00:36:03,320 --> 00:36:04,880
If I answer truthfully

587
00:36:05,070 --> 00:36:06,050
and cooperate with the investigation,

588
00:36:06,050 --> 00:36:07,710
can I get a commuted sentence?

589
00:36:07,880 --> 00:36:10,540
It depends on
whether it meets the regulations.

590
00:36:10,950 --> 00:36:12,230
Whether it's useful or not,

591
00:36:12,230 --> 00:36:14,480
as long as there's a beautiful officer
who chats with me for a while,

592
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:15,880
I'll say whatever I know.

593
00:36:16,880 --> 00:36:19,180
Obstructing police officers
from executing their duties

594
00:36:19,180 --> 00:36:20,710
will be severely punished.

595
00:36:22,970 --> 00:36:24,090
Here are 10 photos.

596
00:36:24,250 --> 00:36:25,650
Which one is Jiang Cheng?

597
00:36:28,330 --> 00:36:29,670
He... he's not in any of them.

598
00:36:29,670 --> 00:36:31,070
He's not in the first row.

599
00:36:32,860 --> 00:36:33,860
What about these?

600
00:36:34,470 --> 00:36:35,200
That one.

601
00:36:35,230 --> 00:36:36,030
The middle one.

602
00:36:36,030 --> 00:36:36,880
That one, yes.

603
00:36:36,880 --> 00:36:37,480
Is it him?

604
00:36:37,480 --> 00:36:37,510
That one. It can't be wrong.

605
00:36:37,510 --> 00:36:38,950
That one. It can't be wrong.

606
00:36:38,950 --> 00:36:40,990
I used to be in the same cell as him.

607
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,590
Then tell us

608
00:36:42,620 --> 00:36:43,790
how

609
00:36:43,810 --> 00:36:44,810
and when you meet?

610
00:36:45,910 --> 00:36:47,110
I can't

611
00:36:47,110 --> 00:36:48,510
remember the exact time.

612
00:36:48,670 --> 00:36:50,480
Anyway, I remember when he first came in,

613
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:52,010
he was in the same cell as me.

614
00:36:52,440 --> 00:36:53,320
Well,

615
00:36:53,350 --> 00:36:55,310
at first, he didn't know anyone

616
00:36:55,510 --> 00:36:57,090
and wouldn't talk to anyone.

617
00:36:57,090 --> 00:36:58,800
So I wasn't familiar with him, either.

618
00:36:58,800 --> 00:37:00,800
But you know, this kind of place

619
00:37:00,830 --> 00:37:02,830
can never keep any secrets.

620
00:37:03,210 --> 00:37:04,850
On his very first day here,

621
00:37:05,070 --> 00:37:07,670
everyone knew he used to be a cop.

622
00:37:08,330 --> 00:37:09,360
None of the people in here

623
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:11,510
don't hate cops.

624
00:37:11,620 --> 00:37:13,270
Right? And he was new.

625
00:37:13,290 --> 00:37:14,350
It was his first time in prison.

626
00:37:14,350 --> 00:37:15,750
So the boss here

627
00:37:15,770 --> 00:37:16,690
often

628
00:37:16,840 --> 00:37:18,240
got people to beat him up.

629
00:37:19,310 --> 00:37:20,410
Jiang Cheng

630
00:37:20,440 --> 00:37:22,290
was kind of a coward at first.

631
00:37:22,520 --> 00:37:24,380
He didn't fight back when beaten.

632
00:37:24,520 --> 00:37:26,470
We even laughed at him behind his back,

633
00:37:26,470 --> 00:37:27,670
saying he was the type

634
00:37:27,820 --> 00:37:30,340
who couldn't act tough
without his uniform.

635
00:37:31,710 --> 00:37:32,710
Since he never spoke up

636
00:37:32,710 --> 00:37:34,070
after getting hit,

637
00:37:34,070 --> 00:37:35,130
the others thought

638
00:37:35,190 --> 00:37:35,960
he was a wimp,

639
00:37:35,980 --> 00:37:37,960
so they had people beat him up every day.

640
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:39,230
Honestly,

641
00:37:39,230 --> 00:37:39,960
with something like this,

642
00:37:39,960 --> 00:37:42,500
if you just swallow your pride
and admit fault,

643
00:37:42,500 --> 00:37:43,750
it'll blow over.

644
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:46,280
I even tried to talk him into it
behind the scenes a few times—

645
00:37:46,280 --> 00:37:48,470
told him to just bow his head
and let it go.

646
00:37:48,470 --> 00:37:51,470
But his temper is really not great.

647
00:37:51,500 --> 00:37:52,430
He's stubborn.

648
00:37:52,510 --> 00:37:54,340
He didn't say a word
and didn't admit defeat

649
00:37:54,340 --> 00:37:56,000
after being beaten like that.

650
00:37:56,220 --> 00:37:57,970
But then again,

651
00:37:58,320 --> 00:38:01,150
you can't push people too far, right?

652
00:38:01,410 --> 00:38:03,670
Tolerating it once or twice is one thing.

653
00:38:03,690 --> 00:38:05,070
Who can tolerate it forever?

654
00:38:05,070 --> 00:38:06,600
How long did he tolerate it?

655
00:38:07,170 --> 00:38:08,570
Probably for about...

656
00:38:08,850 --> 00:38:09,770
about a month.

657
00:38:10,230 --> 00:38:11,690
Someone came to visit him.

658
00:38:12,350 --> 00:38:13,410
After he came back that day,

659
00:38:13,410 --> 00:38:14,740
he wasn't acting right.

660
00:38:15,490 --> 00:38:17,550
He didn't talk and ignored everyone.

661
00:38:20,050 --> 00:38:28,270
[2012]

662
00:38:37,630 --> 00:38:38,590
Jiang Cheng!

663
00:38:38,940 --> 00:38:40,100
Go sit over there.

664
00:39:37,880 --> 00:39:39,410
What happened to your face?

665
00:39:46,930 --> 00:39:47,860
Why?

666
00:39:54,930 --> 00:39:55,660
Jiang Cheng.

667
00:40:00,320 --> 00:40:02,450
I don't believe you'd be hiding drugs.

668
00:40:04,720 --> 00:40:05,780
Someone set you up,

669
00:40:06,680 --> 00:40:07,320
right?

670
00:40:11,150 --> 00:40:12,020
Say something.

671
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:15,690
I'll believe whatever you say.

672
00:40:19,820 --> 00:40:21,330
Say something.

673
00:40:22,980 --> 00:40:24,860
Was someone trying to set you up?

674
00:40:30,330 --> 00:40:32,170
When did you turn into this?

675
00:40:37,170 --> 00:40:38,850
How did I not notice at all?

676
00:40:43,920 --> 00:40:45,360
If there's nothing else,

677
00:40:46,200 --> 00:40:47,860
let's leave it at that for now.

678
00:40:48,420 --> 00:40:49,390
Dad had a stroke.

679
00:40:55,330 --> 00:40:57,570
Except for a little problem with his leg,

680
00:40:57,570 --> 00:40:58,970
everything else is fine.

681
00:41:05,080 --> 00:41:06,880
He asked me to pass you a message.

682
00:41:10,640 --> 00:41:12,100
It's never too late to turn

683
00:41:13,080 --> 00:41:13,940
over a new leaf.

684
00:41:26,650 --> 00:41:28,180
Nothing else to say, right?

685
00:41:34,460 --> 00:41:36,120
The stuff for our engagement—

686
00:41:38,840 --> 00:41:40,040
I'll return it to you.

687
00:41:42,920 --> 00:41:44,580
The banquet will be canceled.

688
00:41:46,080 --> 00:41:47,880
The rings will be returned, too.

689
00:41:53,590 --> 00:41:54,400
And,

690
00:41:58,490 --> 00:42:00,020
the promises you made to me—

691
00:42:03,620 --> 00:42:04,970
I'll forget them all.

692
00:42:16,000 --> 00:42:16,690
Up to you.
